<ab facs="#facs_167_r1l5">Jn <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> cʒurede geſacʒt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . Der hat vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> daʒ er <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
